OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAndrew Ridgeley: I wish    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FWham played a farewell tour
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Wham star Andrew Ridgeley has said he  
OL,6, wishes they had taken their final show 
OL,7, on the road - 37 years to the day from 
OL,8, their farewell gig at Wembley stadium. 
OL,10,FDecisively titled The Final, it came   
OL,11,Fnearly four years after their first    
OL,12,Fhit, Young Guns, and marked the start  
OL,13,Fof bandmate George Michael's solo      
OL,14,Fcareer.                                
OL,16,FBut Ridgeley says he wanted the band's 
OL,17,Ffarewell to have taken a little longer.
OL,19,F"I would have liked to tour The Final  
OL,20,Fto be honest," he tells the BBC.       
